WEBVTT

00:03:59.770 --> 00:04:03.059
Sasa, nafikiri tunaanza kuingia hatua

00:04:03.073 --> 00:04:08.138
ambapo makampuni yameanza kutambua
hii sio tena endelevu,

00:04:08.182 --> 00:04:10.663
na yameanza kuona pingamizi

00:04:10.671 --> 00:04:14.037
hio inatoka kwa 
watu, watumiaji, wananchi,

00:04:14.047 --> 00:04:16.402
lakini pia serikali
zinazoanza kusema,

00:04:16.440 --> 00:04:17.954
"Hii haiwezekani."

00:04:17.994 --> 00:04:23.577
Hivyo nafikiri kuna ukomavu
unaoanza kukaa,

00:04:23.605 --> 00:04:26.104
hasa kwenye hilo eneo la Silicon Valley,

00:04:26.114 --> 00:04:30.148
ambapo watu wameanza kusema,
"Tunajukumu."